Basic Growth Scenario

Cale Basaraba

Introduction

This is a bare bones run of the metaflu simulator.

  • ~15 Chickens (Poisson distribution with 15 as mean)

  • 100 Farms

  • One initial seeded infection

Initial Run

Growth Run

The only change made to this run is that approximately 11% of the original farms grow to ten-times their original size (~15 to ~150), resulting in twice as many chickens in the entire network. For this experiment, the growing farms are chosen at random.
